'''安大略省政府'''是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]]的省级[[政府|政府]]。广义上由省立法机关、省行政机关和省司法机关组成；狭义上特指省行政机关。

== 官方 ==

=== 君主 ===
{{Main|安大略省君主}}
[[加拿大君主|加拿大女皇]][[伊丽莎白二世|伊利沙伯二世]]在安大略省級為[[安大略省君主|以安大略省為權利主體的女皇]]（the Queen in Right of Ontario）。作為[[英聯邦王國|英聯邦王國]]，加拿大與英聯邦內的其他14個獨立國家[[共主邦聯|共戴一君]]。{{refn|<ref>{{cite web| url=https://www.ledevoir.com/documents/pdf/jugement_succession_trone.pdf| title=Jugement No. 200-17-018455-139| publisher=Cour supérieure du Québec| via=[[Le_Devoir|Le Devoir]]| date=2016-02-16| access-date=2016-02-17| author=Claude Bouchard| language=fr| pages=16| archive-date=2020-05-31| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200531153132/https://www.ledevoir.com/documents/pdf/jugement_succession_trone.pdf}}</ref><ref name=evolve>{{cite journal| title=Canada's Evolving Crown: From a British Crown to a "Crown of Maples"| last1=Romaniuk| first1=Scott Nicholas| last2=Wasylciw| first2=Joshua K.| journal=American, British and Canadian Studies Journal| date=February 2015| volume=23| issue=1| pages=108–125| doi=10.1515/abcsj-2014-0030| doi-access=free}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://canadiancrown.gc.ca/DAMAssetPub/DAM-CRN-jblDmt-dmdJbl/STAGING/texte-text/crnMpls_1336157759317_eng.pdf?WT.contentAuthority=4.4.4| title=Crown of Maples: Constitutional Monarchy in Canada| publisher=Her Majesty the Queen in Right of Canada| date=2015| access-date=2016-02-16| author=Department of Canadian Heritage| pages=3| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121110140303/http://canadiancrown.gc.ca/DAMAssetPub/DAM-CRN-jblDmt-dmdJbl/STAGING/texte-text/crnMpls_1336157759317_eng.pdf?WT.contentAuthority=4.4.4| archive-date=2012-11-10| url-status=dead}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchAndCommonwealth/Canada/TheQueensroleinCanada.aspx| title=Queen and Canada| publisher=The Royal Household| access-date=2016-02-16| archive-date=2009-02-20| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090220102227/http://www.royal.gov.uk/MonarchAndCommonwealth/Canada/TheQueensroleinCanada.aspx}}</ref><ref>{{cite web| url=http://canada.pch.gc.ca/eng/1444999464289| title=The Queen of Canada| publisher=Government of Canada| access-date=2016-02-16| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224135322/http://canada.pch.gc.ca/eng/1444999464289| archive-date=2016-02-24| url-status=dead}}</ref>}}在加拿大，君主代表聯邦政府及10個省單獨行使權力。聯邦的君主制及各省的君主制各自獨立，互不干涉。

=== 省督 ===
{{Main|安大略省省督}}
安大略省[[官方_(法人)|官方]]的權力屬於安大略省君主，但下放予[[安大略省省督|安大略省省督]]行使。省長及行政會議的建議通常具有約束力；《[[1867年憲法法令|1867年憲法法令]]》規定行政權力只能「由行政會議並在行政會議的建議下」行使。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Consolidated federal laws of canada, THE CONSTITUTION ACTS, 1867 to 1982|url=https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/const/page-2.html#h-11|access-date=2021-04-03|date=2020-08-07|last=Branch|first=Legislative Services|website=laws-lois.justice.gc.ca|archive-date=2022-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220605145518/https://laws-lois.justice.gc.ca/eng/const/page-2.html#h-11}}</ref>

== 立法机关 ==

[[安大略省議會|安大略省議會]]是安大略省的立法机关，负责[[加拿大宪法|加拿大宪法]]和其他法律规定的属于本省管辖范围内的立法工作，监督本省行政机关等事务。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.ola.org/en/offices-divisions-branches/about-us |title=About us - Legislative Assembly of Ontario |access-date=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226105642/https://www.ola.org/en/offices-divisions-branches/about-us |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 行政机关 ==

=== 省行政会议（内阁） ===
省行政会议（内阁）由省长、省行政机关各组成部门主管（各厅厅长）及其他必要人员组成。内阁成员由省长向省督建议，由省督任命；内阁成员通常为省议会议员。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.sdc.gov.on.ca/sites/mgcs-onterm/en/Pages/rl_0010.aspx |title=Ministers - Executive Council of Ontario |access-date=2020-10-02 |archive-date=2020-12-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201201155309/https://www.sdc.gov.on.ca/sites/mgcs-onterm/en/Pages/rl_0010.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

本届省行政会议现时组成人员共29人。

